Author: aerienne
Text: I take benedryl every night for this very reason, but these past few days were awful. I was busy and stayed up to get work done, but ugh it sucked. Hoping today breaks that cycle.

Author: must_stay_awake
Text: THIS is precisely why I drug myself into a sleep coma with ZQuil every night. I wish I had a better answer for you (and also in no way recommend that because now I can't sleep without it...fun!)
